{"tid":819874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【狂賀】iPhone Xs Max 爆「Cut 單潮」","createTime":"2018-09-15T06:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T06:59:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4478f7f46cf032036ff7996428050a0fe058d67d","tid":819874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"iPhone Xs/iPhone Xs Max 首日預購，不過香港區卻出現「奇景」！那就是首日晚上訂機的出貨時間竟然比日間還要早？<br />\n<br />\n首賣日下午 3 : 01 至 3 時 30 分，基本上大多數訂單也是首批出貨，最早 9 月 22 日。不過其後就變成 10 月份出貨，但到了晚上 AOS 新的訂單又變成 9 月22日出貨。部份用家大感意外，不少人因為想早點拿到 iPhone 而被迫「Cut 單」重新再訂一次，令發貨時間提早。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: red;\">不少「炒家」眼見 iPhone Xs Max 的 iReserve 開了太長的時間仍有供應，因此將大量的 AOS 單也取消！</span>而 Apple 也重新將多出來的貨供給新的買家預購。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/09/15/aos-cut-order/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2Faos-cut-order%2F&d=YimojzN41BgOjYFUyOKT3AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=340d02ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/09/15/aos-cut-order/</a>"},{"pid":"15cbf235d9cab6affc44f0be4b33cb4393ff7311","tid":819874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"World No iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527ca01cafd729881c09f0706c18acfe9b4ec514","tid":819874,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"香港生果store全線執笠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508419141a79dcd357e3ed256721e8b0dcd5bb32","tid":819874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"527ca01cafd729881c09f0706c18acfe9b4ec514","tid":819874,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"香港生果store全線執笠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-1